               <msContents>
                  <summary>Gospel of John, ወንጌል፡ ዘዮሐንስ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1"><locus from="1r" to="89v" facs="003">Fols 1r–89v</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1693John">Gospel of John</title>
                     <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ‘ǝz</textLang>
                     <note>Text begins on <locus target="#1r" facs="003">fols. 1r, </locus>; conclusion (mäl’a), <locus target="#89r" facs="091">89r, </locus>.A crude hand has marked in blue ink the days of the week for reading (<locus target="#1r #6v #7v #9r #11v" facs="003 009 010 011 014">1r, 6v, 7v, 9r, 11v</locus> etc.). Another hand has introduced extensive corrections</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
